definitions.definition: A container for transporting meals, especially lunch .
The male genitals when enclosed in clothing.
A lunch packaged in a disposable box to be taken away to eat.
examples: Jack was carrying his lunchbox with him.

definitions.definition: A luggable ; an early laptop computer , usually a unit with a handle and a fold-out keyboard .
A simple portable transmitter sometimes used in phreaking .
A cocktail made with beer , orange juice , and almond liqueur .
A person seen as weak and disposable who could easily be sacrificed without much guilt or afterthought .
